{"tid":793794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【明晚港姐決賽】何泳芍三點式騷弗爆身材 健康膚色成摘后冠障礙","createTime":"2018-08-25T16:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T09:22:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9146b0d1738ad8a64c644f3b58514e9facaba9f7","tid":793794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180825/s00007/6ae93297f7e447c85f91aa1347207cc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180825%2Fs00007%2F6ae93297f7e447c85f91aa1347207cc3.jpg&h=16b9f61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【今日直擊】《2018香港小姐競選決賽》明晚舉行，今日20位候選港姐，再以泳裝作最後綵排。當中以（14）何泳芍（Honey）身形弗爆，而且自信滿滿。Honey被問到是否身形最有優勢？她說：「是嗎？多謝﹗（最有信心是泳衣環節？）好多Part我都有信心，本身有做運動，操得較弗，而且職業關係（潛水教練）我會多著泳衣，會比較自在。」<br />\n<br />\n以往港姐冠軍的膚色白晳，而Honey擁有健康膚色，會否反而成為障礙呢？她說：「評判方面我不擔心，上年冠軍雷莊𠒇和我膚色較接近，當然我（膚色）比她黑，自信好重要，投票方面，我覺得我因為膚色健康，而多了好多票，多了人認得我，或看過我報道，因為之前我在social media都有Po過，好多女仔跟我說，我和你的經歷都好似，她們對我支持好忠實。（是否優勢？）是的，我覺得是優勢。」<br />\n<br />\n談到決賽最大對手，她指（7）丁子田﹑（10）李芷晴和（20）鄧卓殷，都非常有自信，大家在綵排時都有留意彼此的表現。"},{"pid":"10fa7e57d0a4033f5bb81e0d1bf34e542c0afe56","tid":793794,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346164ce7998c1d6856cfe7f60dbc26ff10f3644","tid":793794,"uid":15815,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"仲睇大台港姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n30年前咩"},{"pid":"1b5c0dd9b0d6194015e9f2b30857bca0a76e4c0a","tid":793794,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"說好的弗爆呢"},{"pid":"10b1d483dfb37fb2c048c4fc991f2b7dec90fa6f","tid":793794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346164ce7998c1d6856cfe7f60dbc26ff10f3644","tid":793794,"uid":15815,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"仲睇大台港姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n30年前咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"一秒都無睇<br />\n<br />\n睇明報"},{"pid":"ab5f48419c2ba1d29f7cbbe85b042dedfea000db","tid":793794,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"其實港姐既目的係咪比錢佬睇版？"},{"pid":"2217b4bd97f009a4399be2d3069d939dd29bebc9","tid":793794,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d9409c1a8bf2e3c937538851b25e088e6a720fa","tid":793794,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2217b4bd97f009a4399be2d3069d939dd29bebc9","tid":793794,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:51:35.000Z","msg":"新花都D名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d53c35e7a1082972841907e43ea59199471aa4","tid":793794,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"假波？"},{"pid":"75e854c3b30fd8dfbbe8b4b478046de336e7eb4c","tid":793794,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"7號無懸念吧"},{"pid":"c0f5999409dd8aeb663817885318d502ee762d9a","tid":793794,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346164ce7998c1d6856cfe7f60dbc26ff10f3644","tid":793794,"uid":15815,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"仲睇大台港姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n30年前咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"應該問「仲睇大台？」<br />\n以前無線唯一睇就係動畫同無線新聞，大個咗返工冇睇動畫。<br />\n無線新聞自旺角騷亂開始已經冇睇，唔係被逼睇（例如阿婆食飯，茶記播）我都唔會睇。<br />\n就算去外地無即時電視新聞睇，寧願隔幾小時去youtube睇其他台新聞。"